CZECH CNB FIXES CROWN + 3 . 15 PCT VS MARK / USD BASKET . The Czech National Bank ( CNB ) fixed the crown at 26 . 432 to the dollar after Tuesday ' s fixing at 26 . 052 , and at 17 . 811 to the mark from 17 . 628 . The above rates imply a deviation from the midpoint of the central bank ' s mark / dollar basket of + 3 . 15 percent , after a deviation of + 4 . 05 on Tuesday . During the minute at which the central bank calculated today ' s fixing , the crown was trading on the interbank market at + 3 . 13 percent . The crown fixing is announced daily at about 1140 CET ( 0940 GMT ) , and is within plus / minus 7 . 5 percent of the mid - point of a mark / dollar basket midpoint calculated between 11 : 30 : 00 and 11 : 30 : 59 CET . - - Prague Newsroom , 42 - 2 - 2423 - 0003 
